Description: Lorica Linux base hardening configuration
 Security hardening for Debian servers. Installs drop-in configuration
 files for sysctl, GRUB boot parameters, kernel module blacklisting,
 and audit rules. Every setting is documented with its rationale and
 mapped to compliance frameworks (CIS, PCI-DSS, SOC 2, CNBV).
 .
